title: There has to be some sort of mistake...
body: I am Silver 4,Honour level 2 and I have not received any of my ranked rewards?

replies.body: It's possible that some players may not have received their end-of-season rewards just yet. Riot's plan (as per the "[End-of-Season Information](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/360010365913)" support page) is to have them all out by the 12th of December, so you may just be among the last players to actually receive them. I'd say you probably just want to keep an eye on it for the time being, and if you haven't received your rewards by the 12-13th of December, you can submit a ticket to [Support](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) (use the "2018 Season Ranked and Honor rewards" option) and address the issue with them.

Just to tack on, this is assuming you were Honour 2 at season end. If you only reached Honour 2 *after* season end, then [THIS POST](https://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/developer-corner/TGYs0hwO-2018-end-of-season-rewards-and-honor) is where you'll find your info on whether you are eligible for season rewards or not.
